1. *Prestala* je kiša da pada. (The rain has stopped falling.)
2. Kad je *prestala* da radi, ostala mi je u sećanju kao najbolja koleginica. (When she stopped working, she remained in my memory as the best colleague.)
3. Ona je *prestala* da se bavi sportom pre pet godina. (She stopped doing sports five years ago.)
4. Kada je *prestala* da puši, osećala se mnogo bolje. (When she stopped smoking, she felt much better.)
5. Kada se *prestala* čuti muzika, svi su ustali i krenuli kući. (When the music stopped playing, everyone stood up and headed home.)
6. *Prestala* je da govori o tome kada je videla da joj niko ne veruje. (She stopped talking about it when she saw that no one believed her.)
7. Bilo je potrebno da *prestaneš* da se nerviraš zbog sitnica. (You needed to stop getting upset over trivial things.)
8. Nadam se da ćeš uskoro *prestati* da pušiš. (I hope you will stop smoking soon.)
9. Oni su *prestali* da dolaze na treninge jer su se osećali zapostavljeno. (They stopped coming to trainings because they felt neglected.)
10. Neću *prestati* dok ne dođem do cilja. (I won't stop until I reach my goal.)